1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:05,680
Ndifuna ukukubonisa indlela yokuphanda ngayo nantoni na kuba uphando lunamandla.

2
00:00:05,680 --> 00:00:10,000
Kwakhona bubuchule yaye xa ufunda indlela yokwenza oko, unokuzifundisa ngokwakho

3
00:00:10,000 --> 00:00:11,000
nantoni na oyifunayo.

4
00:00:11,000 --> 00:00:14,760
Yaye ukuba uye waqonda kutshanje ukuba abantu abaninzi abakwazi ukwenza uphando, bayazi ukuba

5
00:00:14,760 --> 00:00:15,760
ukufuna.

6
00:00:15,760 --> 00:00:19,880
Kwaye kukho ngokwenene umahluko omkhulu kakhulu kuba xa ukhangela, uthembele kwabanye

7
00:00:19,880 --> 00:00:22,440
abantu bacinge ngawe kwaye asifuni oko.

8
00:00:22,440 --> 00:00:23,840
Sifuna ukwenza ngcono.

9
00:00:23,840 --> 00:00:26,080
Ngoko ewe, uphando lunamanqanaba.

10
00:00:26,080 --> 00:00:29,560
Inkqubo yam endiyisebenzisayo ineenkqubo ezine, ngoko ndiza kukucacisela ngazo.

11
00:00:29,560 --> 00:00:31,680
Enye yazo kukhangela kwakho umphezulu.

12
00:00:31,680 --> 00:00:35,600
Le yindawo ekufuneka uqale kuyo, kodwa abantu abaninzi bayayeka.

13
00:00:35,600 --> 00:00:41,760
Oku kukhangelo lwakho kuGoogle, iividiyo zeTikTok, iinkcazo zeYouTube, iimpendulo ze-AI.

14
00:00:41,760 --> 00:00:46,519
Yaye ingxaki yokuma apha kukuba ufumana izigqibo ezixineneyo kwaye

15
00:00:46,519 --> 00:00:48,640
Abazange bayiqonde indlela ezazakhiwa ngayo.

16
00:00:48,640 --> 00:00:49,640
Ngoko makhe sithathe umzekelo.

17
00:00:49,640 --> 00:00:55,000
Masithi ukhangela ukuba yintoni into emnyama kwaye ufumana iziphumo ezifana, kakuhle,

18
00:00:55,000 --> 00:00:57,600
yenza i-85% yendalo iphela.

19
00:00:57,600 --> 00:00:58,760
Asinakuyibona.

20
00:00:58,760 --> 00:01:00,520
Oku kuchaphazela amandla obunzima.

21
00:01:00,520 --> 00:01:05,120
Uyazi zonke ezi nyaniso, kodwa usengaziqondi izinto ezinjengokuthi sazi njani ukuba

22
00:01:05,120 --> 00:01:11,440
kukho okanye bubungqina obunjani obubuxhasa ngokwenene okanye ziziphi iimbono ezikhuphisanayo?

23
00:01:11,440 --> 00:01:13,480
Ngoko uyenza njani inqanaba lokuqala ngokuchanekileyo?

24
00:01:13,480 --> 00:01:17,400
Uyisebenzisa njengesikhokelo sakho kungekhona semfundo.

25
00:01:17,400 --> 00:01:23,560
Ngoko injongo yakho kweli nqanaba kufuneka ibe kukufunda isigama, ukuchonga iingcamango ezingundoqo

26
00:01:23,560 --> 00:01:27,760
uze uzenzele imibuzo engakumbi, ufumanise into ongakwaziyo

27
00:01:27,760 --> 00:01:29,920
into osenokuba nomdla kuyo.

28
00:01:29,920 --> 00:01:34,800
Uchitha imizuzu eli-10 ukuya kweli-15 usenza uphando kwinqanaba lokuqala, ubuninzi.

29
00:01:34,800 --> 00:01:39,000
Emva koko uyeka uze uzibuze, yintoni endingayiqondiyo?

30
00:01:39,000 --> 00:01:42,160
Yaye loo mbuzo uyindlela yakho yokufikelela kwinqanaba lesibini.

31
00:01:42,160 --> 00:01:44,760
Inqanaba lesibini lulwandiso lwemithombo.

32
00:01:44,760 --> 00:01:47,160
Kulapho uqala khona ukuphanda.

33
00:01:47,160 --> 00:01:48,760
Ngoko le nto ibukeka njani?

34
00:01:48,760 --> 00:01:51,880
Oku kukucofa kwimithombo namanqaku.

35
00:01:51,880 --> 00:01:55,520
Kufundwa izifundo ezipheleleyo endaweni nje yesishwankathelo.

36
00:01:55,520 --> 00:01:59,120
Landela amakhonkco kunye neenkcazo kunye neerekhodi.

37
00:01:59,120 --> 00:02:00,520
Kulapho usuka khona.

38
00:02:00,520 --> 00:02:01,520
Yintoni le?

39
00:02:01,520 --> 00:02:03,520
Ivela phi le nto?

40
00:02:03,520 --> 00:02:05,680
Makhe sibuyele kumzekelo wezinto ezimnyama.

41
00:02:05,680 --> 00:02:08,640
Ngoku awusahlali kuGoogle okanye kwiTikTok.

42
00:02:08,640 --> 00:02:10,759
Uvula iphepha leNASA.

43
00:02:10,759 --> 00:02:12,640
Ucofa kuphando olukhankanyiweyo.

44
00:02:12,640 --> 00:02:18,520
Uvula i-Galaxy Rotation Curve Study kwaye ubona ukubonwa ngu

45
00:02:18,520 --> 00:02:19,520
izazinzulu.

46
00:02:19,520 --> 00:02:24,400
Ngoko le nto ibaluleke kakhulu kuba ngoku ubona ubungqina kungekhona nje isiphumo.

47
00:02:24,400 --> 00:02:28,080
Ngoko uvula njani ukuze uvule yonke into ngendlela efanelekileyo?

48
00:02:28,080 --> 00:02:29,640
Musa ukufunda nje iphepha uze ulivale.

49
00:02:29,640 --> 00:02:33,600
Umele ube neethebhu ezintlanu ukuya kwezilishumi ezivulekileyo kuyo yonke into oyijongayo.

50
00:02:33,600 --> 00:02:36,400
Kufuneka ulandele izicatshulwa ngoku.

51
00:02:36,400 --> 00:02:41,760
Ngoko ukusuka kwinqaku ukuya kwisifundo ukuya kwidatha yoqobo, konke oko kusoloko kuhle

52
00:02:41,760 --> 00:02:42,760
Zidibene kakhulu.

53
00:02:42,760 --> 00:02:49,760
Kufuneka ubeke phambili.edu's.gov's, amaphepha apapashiweyo, naziphi na iziqulatho ezivela kwingcali kwi

54
00:02:49,760 --> 00:02:50,760
intsimi.

55
00:02:50,760 --> 00:02:56,000
Yaye ufanele uzibuze, yintoni le nto ndiyifunayo?

56
00:02:56,000 --> 00:02:59,799
Kuba ukuba awukwazi ukuphendula loo mbuzo, kusenokwenzeka ukuba usabuyela kwinqanaba lokuqala.

57
00:02:59,799 --> 00:03:02,959
Ndingene kwinqanaba lesithathu, elibizwa ngokuba kukuchongwa kwemifanekiso.

58
00:03:02,959 --> 00:03:07,519
Kwaye ndicinga ukuba le yinqanaba apho inyaniso iqala ukubonakala ngokwenene kuba

59
00:03:07,520 --> 00:03:13,040
kweli nqanaba, ugxininiso lwakho oluphambili kukuthelekisa imithombo emininzi kwaye unikela ingqalelo

60
00:03:13,040 --> 00:03:16,000
ukuvumelana nokungqubana phakathi kwabo.

61
00:03:16,000 --> 00:03:19,880
Ubona iingcamango eziphindaphindiweyo ozibonayo.

62
00:03:19,880 --> 00:03:25,200
Ufuna ngokwenene izinto ezibonakala ngokuphindaphindiweyo phezu kwabo imithombo, nokuba

63
00:03:25,200 --> 00:03:31,480
amanani okanye imibuzo okanye iingcamango okanye iingxoxo kuba ibonisa ukuba zibalulekile.

64
00:03:31,480 --> 00:03:35,160
Masithi ufunda ngemithombo emithandathu eyahlukeneyo yemathiriyeli emnyama.

65
00:03:35,160 --> 00:03:39,359
Kwaye ezintandathu zazo zathi ukujikeleza kwegalaksi akuhambelani nobunzima obubonakalayo kwaye enye yazo

66
00:03:39,359 --> 00:03:41,800
wathi mhlawumbi imithetho yomxhuzulane ayilunganga.

67
00:03:41,800 --> 00:03:46,280
Ngoko ke ngoku ubona ngokwenene ukuvumelana kwenzeka ngaphakathi isihloko ngokwayo.

68
00:03:46,280 --> 00:03:51,240
Ubona izinto ezingaqhelekanga kwaye ubona iingxoxo ezikhoyo kwaye uqala ukufumana real

69
00:03:51,240 --> 00:03:53,280
ukuqonda oko ufunda ngako.

70
00:03:53,280 --> 00:03:56,720
Naliphi na inqanaba, ezintathu ngokufanelekileyo, ukhangela ukudibana.

71
00:03:56,720 --> 00:03:59,000
Ngoko yintoni enokuvumelana ngayo inkoliso yemithombo?

72
00:03:59,000 --> 00:04:01,640
Kwakhona ufanele uqaphele ukungavisisani.

73
00:04:01,640 --> 00:04:05,720
Ngoko khawuqwalasele apho iingcali zingavumelaniyo khona ngalo mbandela.

74
00:04:05,720 --> 00:04:07,920
Umele ulungise ubungqina obufumanayo.

75
00:04:07,920 --> 00:04:11,880
Unokuwahlula abe bubungqina obuqinileyo kunokucinga.

76
00:04:11,880 --> 00:04:17,039
Unokwenza neebhakethi ezintathu zengqondo okanye uzibhale phantsi ukuba ufuna.

77
00:04:17,039 --> 00:04:22,039
Kodwa enye yazo lulwazi olufumanayo oluhambelana kuyo yonke imithombo.

78
00:04:22,039 --> 00:04:27,680
Enye ngolwazi oluphikiswayo yaye enye ngolwazi olungaqinisekanga.

79
00:04:27,680 --> 00:04:32,020
Yaye ngokwenza oko, ufunda wena ngokwakho kwaye wakha eyakho ingqiqo

80
00:04:32,020 --> 00:04:33,720
ukugweba ngalo mbandela.

81
00:04:33,720 --> 00:04:38,960
Inqanaba lobunzulu kunye nenqanaba lesakhelo kuba kulapho uyeka khona ukufunda ulwazi

82
00:04:38,960 --> 00:04:41,800
kwaye uqala ukucinga ngeenkqubo.

83
00:04:41,800 --> 00:04:43,520
Ubuza imibuzo engcono.

84
00:04:43,520 --> 00:04:48,400
Uyakha iimodeli zengqondo zomxholo owenza uphando ngawo kwaye uqala

85
00:04:48,400 --> 00:04:52,800
ukudibanisa iingcamango kwiinkalo ezahlukeneyo zophando.

86
00:04:52,800 --> 00:04:58,000
Ngoko ufuna ngokwenene ulwakhiwo olusemva komxholo wento oyiphandayo.

87
00:04:58,000 --> 00:05:02,680
Endaweni yokubuza ukuba yintoni into emnyama, sibuza imibuzo enzulu.

88
00:05:02,680 --> 00:05:08,000
Sibuza izinto ezifana nesizathu sokuba ubunzima buziphathe ngale ndlela okanye ziziphi iimbono ezakhiwe

89
00:05:08,000 --> 00:05:13,480
kwimizekelo yethu ekhoyo yemathiriyeli emnyama okanye oko bekuya kuba yinyani kuko konke oku

90
00:05:13,480 --> 00:05:15,480
ukuba ndiphosakele.

91
00:05:15,480 --> 00:05:20,360
Uyaziqeqesha ngokwenene ukuba ucinge nzulu uze ubuze imibuzo engcono,

92
00:05:20,360 --> 00:05:22,360
