93
00:05:22,360 --> 00:05:27,880
Umgangatho sibuza imibuzo yesibini umyalelo, asibuzi nje ntoni, kodwa kutheni kwaye kutheni

94
00:05:27,880 --> 00:05:31,160
Kuthekani ukuba sakha kwiimodeli zethu zengqondo?

95
00:05:31,160 --> 00:05:34,120
Ngoko thabatha iphepha uze ulibhukishe phambi kwakho, akunjalo?

96
00:05:34,120 --> 00:05:37,120
Into emnyama, yindawo yokungabikho kwezibalo.

97
00:05:37,120 --> 00:05:39,000
Kuqhutywa kwiziphumo zomxhuzulane.

98
00:05:39,000 --> 00:05:41,200
Ayibonakali ngokuthe ngqo.

99
00:05:41,200 --> 00:05:44,920
Yenza umzobo ukuze ubone imephu yayo uze uqalise ukuyiqhagamshela.

100
00:05:44,920 --> 00:05:46,080
Into emnyama yinzululwazi.

101
00:05:46,080 --> 00:05:47,240
Yinkcubeko.

102
00:05:47,240 --> 00:05:49,280
Yintanda-bulumko yenzululwazi.

103
00:05:49,280 --> 00:05:54,960
Unokuthatha inkcazelo onayo uze uyithathe ube bubungqina, into engaqinisekanga,

104
00:05:54,960 --> 00:05:58,559
oko malunga nesihloko kukuba umda wolwazi lwethu.

105
00:05:58,559 --> 00:06:02,599
Xa uqala ukuyibeka phambi kwakho uze wakhe imodeli uqala ukuyibona

106
00:06:02,599 --> 00:06:06,320
zonke izixhumanisi kwaye uqala ukubona zonke izikhewu ezingekhoyo.

107
00:06:06,320 --> 00:06:10,159
Yaye kububudenge ukuba loo nto ikunceda kangakanani ukuba uyiqonde.

108
00:06:10,159 --> 00:06:13,599
Eyona nto iphambili ngophando kukuba aluyondawo, luyingqungquthela.

109
00:06:13,599 --> 00:06:17,719
Ngoko ukhangela uze wandise uze uthelekise uze wakhe ezo ngqondo

110
00:06:17,720 --> 00:06:18,720
iimodeli.

111
00:06:18,720 --> 00:06:21,240
Yaye kwiimodeli zengqondo ufumana imibuzo engcono.

112
00:06:21,240 --> 00:06:25,640
Emva koko uyiphindaphinda yonke into kwakhona ngemibuzo engcono oyifunayo kwaye uyandisa

113
00:06:25,640 --> 00:06:28,680
uphinde uthelekise uze wakhe ezinye iimodeli.

114
00:06:28,680 --> 00:06:31,720
Yaye ngaloo ndlela ufunda ukucinga ngokwakho.

115
00:06:31,720 --> 00:06:34,680
Ngaloo ndlela uqala ngokwenene ukuqonda into ethile.

116
00:06:34,680 --> 00:06:39,000
Ngaloo ndlela ukulandela ukwazi kwakho kuba namandla kakhulu.

